Move the attatched folder to c:/xampp/htdocs or to the path where you keep your own website projects

Delivery System version 1.0:

1. Open up localhost/JD4/store.html on the browser.

2. Check the active drivers and feed in their current locations. Default current location is Just Delivery Office.
(You'll have to manually feed the current location each time as we are not using any API to get current location yet.)
Activate the drivers.

3. Type in the Source Location and Destination Area and check if the order is self order or not.

4.Select either Undelivered or All in Get Orders field to see the list of orders and order details.
(On any update, change the undelivered to all and all to undelivered to see the successful update. I'll fix this bug in next version.)

5. Show/Suggest button will how the current path each driver has to take in order to make trip shortest and deliver orders in time.
   It will also suggest whom to assign a particular order to.

6. Order Id can be used to change the status of the order or to assign that particular order to any driver.




Version 1.1 will:
1. Include auto refreshing of the page.
2. Bug fixing as mentioned in point 4.
3. More interactive front-end.
4. Better performance.
5. Multiple driver suggestions.